{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Engage in the Devil's turn-base puzzle]<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Gif_Main_Gameplay_2.gif?t=1734628883\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ensure your victims are as desperate as possible by giving them: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Jealousy</strong>, <strong>Sadness</strong>, <strong>Delicious food</strong>, <strong>Paranoia</strong>, divine judgment, and <strong>Bad luck</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Put your victims through different stages]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>-&quot;Break them, make them insane if you must but bring me their souls&quot;</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Final_Giref_GIF_Framed.gif?t=1734628883\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[What Offer would bring to the table?]</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>- \u201dPromise them the whole world, and make one hell of a Deal!\u201d</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Final_Contract_Framed_GIF.gif?t=1734628883\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more desperate the victims are the less you have to offer, and the more you could ask for. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Seek the Church Blessing] </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Curch_Gif_Final_Framed.gif?t=1734628883\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>-&quot;At a small cost&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Have you steel your resolve?]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>-&quot; If not, just use your victim's resolve against them&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Final_2_GIF_Mirror_Framed.gif?t=1734628883\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Losing a bet with the Grim Reaper\u00a0lead you to rot in hell forever. The End.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Well, it seems not even forever isn\u2019t as long as it used to be... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since you got out with a little help, but of course, it wasn't for free.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1726100?t=1734628883","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1726100?t=1734628883","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734628883","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734628883","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages: Suicide, Psychological torture, Light gore, Sexual Insinuation, Revealing clothing, Blood, and drugs insinuation."},"demos":[{"appid":3286550,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Engage in the Devil's turn-base puzzle]<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726100/extras/Gif_Main_Gameplay_2.gif?t=1734628883\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ensure your victims are as desperate as possible by giving them: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Jealousy</strong>, <strong>Sadness</strong>, <strong>Delicious food</strong>, <strong>Paranoia</strong>, divine judgment, and <strong>Bad luck</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Put your victims through different stages]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>-&quot;Break th